    "Central to all these efforts is the fostering of a critical and ethical approach to AI.",
    "Ethical discussions should be an integral part of the learning process, encouraging students to contemplate AI's societal impact.",
    "Case studies and hypothetical scenarios can be utilized to explore the potential benefits and challenges of AI applications.",
    "Moreover, assessments in AI literacy should test not only technical knowledge but also the ability to critically evaluate the role and impact of Artificial Intelligence.",
    "The advancement of prompt engineering within educational settings offers a unique avenue for enriching the learning experience for both teachers and students."
